{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679460/extras/PRF_Social_Accolades_3840x2500_v05.png?t=1736331314\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>We've temporarily removed showing 'Spanish - Latin America' as a supported language on the store page, but worry not if you're from that region. We'll be adding support in a post-launch patch as a free update, so you will still be able to enjoy the game in your chosen language.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From the creative minds behind Persona 3, 4, and 5 comes Metaphor: ReFantazio, a unique fantasy world, where your protagonist will journey alongside his fairy companion, Gallica, to lift the curse from the kingdom\u2019s lost prince. Control your destiny, face your fears and awaken magical &quot;Archetype&quot; powers that lie dormant in your heart. By awakening to an \u201cArchetype,\u201d you will unlock the power to channel and combine the abilities of unique job classes. Strengthen your bonds and build your party to take down powerful foes and discover the kingdom\u2019s true nature.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679460/extras/PRF_Accolades_16x9_SteamB.png?t=1736331314\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Key Features: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Go on quests, dungeon dive, &amp; hunt for treasures by day. Strengthen relationships, build bonds, &amp; increase virtues by night. Choose your actions wisely, time management is key to achieving your goal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679460/extras/01_about_en.gif?t=1736331314\" />-Ride your \u201cgauntlet runner\u201d to faraway dungeons &amp; towns across an expansive world. Discover beautiful landscapes\u202f accompanied by captivating music, immersive UI, &amp; anime cutscenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679460/extras/03_gauntlet_runner_en.gif?t=1736331314\" />-A unique battle system combining turn based &amp; real time action grants strategy &amp; exhilaration at every turn. Party customization through \u201cArchetypes\u201d provides freedom to personalize your adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679460/extras/04_battle_en.gif?t=1736331314\" />-A mysterious &amp; exciting story unfolds in a world where people must fight their own anxiety. Join the high-stakes Royal Tournament that promises hours of captivating exploration and discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679460/extras/02_ordinary_en.gif?t=1736331314\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679460/extras/05_35th_logo_en.png?t=1736331314\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Traveller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2679460/d45d7e7f964851e111a7d00b6344f4641b6ee81a.jpg"},{"name":"Coronation of the King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2679460/4a37a7a22ac7d45cf6d70470ad2d206c4c2cf563.jpg"},{"name":"Allies United","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2679460/e976563b0059d45f8c1b4baf8822f4aaa8dd6e6f.jpg"},{"name":"Out of the Fire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2679460/556bd61ef59cacadc761df2c838b71ff6c8f2e2f.jpg"},{"name":"Calamity Averted","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2679460/7aae5c253593970b7eb6ad90d8e2b7a9090669eb.jpg"},{"name":"Dark Truths","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2679460/583c6a8972a5a425eff9639d1ffdcd8511e3f8f7.jpg"},{"name":"On Knife's Edge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2679460/2c35c4ca2ee6688220228b353b1f91d63f90f587.jpg"},{"name":"History Untold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2679460/ab85c40ad1fbe7ba091116e4f5ef4dbf4f3cdbf2.jpg"},{"name":"Mission Accomplished","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2679460/e96a7ec5b34777dc9ebeea1eadb9c28eace61c52.jpg"},{"name":"Skybound Hope","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2679460/c8d5b8455047c28b0b96aa1cafbbb67c95c6bbec.jpg"}],"total":44},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679460/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736331314","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679460/page.bg.jpg?t=1736331314","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679460/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736331314","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679460/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736331314","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Trading Cards","id":29},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,2,5],"notes":"Game contains violence, blood & gore, partial nudity, and suggestive themes. "},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3130330,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>Metaphor: ReFantazio Atlus 35th Digital Anniversary Edition</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679460/extras/Metaphor_SteamMetadata_Glamshot_English_616_v2.png?t=1736331314\" /